See Consecration

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
See Consecration -- Allows you to identify consecrated items by sight.
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This ritual lets you feel the connection between inanimate objects and your deity, 
making you able to tell at a glance whether they have been consecrated to the deity 
or not.  
.EP
